<section class="hero">
  <span class="hero__eyebrow">Terms</span>
  <h1 class="hero__title">Terms for direct-download access and account billing.</h1>
  <p class="hero__copy">
    Voxlane is sold as an account-based subscription with access managed by the website and reflected in the macOS app.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="section-card">
  <ul style="margin-top: 12px;">
    <li>Access to Pro features depends on the current account entitlement state.</li>
    <li>Trials and paid status are tied to the account email you use to sign in.</li>
    <li>Billing changes, cancellations, and payment methods are managed through Stripe-hosted pages.</li>
    <li>Direct downloads and updates are delivered from Voxlane infrastructure outside the Mac App Store.</li>
    <li>Support requests can be sent to <a href="mailto:<%= AppConfig.support_email %>"><%= AppConfig.support_email %></a>.</li>
  </ul>
</section>
